snippet.title: Seal Online Eternal Destiny - 4 Heroes
snippet.description:
Introduction of 4 class that available in Seal Online Eternal Destiny
Knight - Priest - Hunter - Craftsman
Pick a story of 4 heroes from Shiltz as inspiration..
That's it.. Hope you find it interesting and enjoy..!!

I DO NOT OWN THE SONG.. all credits go to their respective owner..

PS : I'm back after hiatus for roughly 6 months.. here my early Christmas present for you..!!
*Special appearance of Reborn the Apostle*
